  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  GMFCS level III, IV, V of the Cerebral palsy

          -  20-45 degree of Cobb's angle

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  less than 20 degree or more than 45 degree of Cobb's angle

          -  Neuromuscular disease including congenital myopathy, spinal muscular atrophy, muscular
             dystrophy and poliomyelitis

          -  Acute lumbar pain

          -  Fixed scoliosis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
